msgid "Get available link sources for quick-add"
msgstr "Obtenir les sources de lien disponibles pour l'ajout rapide"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Returns available pages and categories for quick-adding as menu items.\n"
"\n"
"    **Query Parameters:**\n"
"    - `type`: Filter by source type (`pages`, `categories`, or `all`)\n"
"    - `search`: Search term to filter results\n"
"\n"
"    **Use Cases:**\n"
"    - Populate quick-add panel in menu builder\n"
"    - Search for pages/categories to add as menu items\n"
"\n"
"    **Authentication:** Staff session required\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Retourne les pages et catégories disponibles pour un ajout rapide en "
"tant qu'éléments de menu. **Paramètres de requête :** - `type` : Filtre par "
"type de source (`pages`, `categories` ou `all`) - `search` : Terme de "
"recherche pour filtrer les résultats **Cas d'utilisation :** - Remplir le "
"panneau d'ajout rapide dans le constructeur de menu - Rechercher des pages/"
"catégories à ajouter en tant qu'éléments de menu **Authentification :** "
"Session d'employé requise\n"
"    "

msgid "Type of sources to return"
msgstr "Type de sources à retourner"

msgid "Search term to filter results"
msgstr "Terme de recherche pour filtrer les résultats"

msgid "Available link sources"
msgstr "Sources de lien disponibles"

msgid "Get rendered menu preview HTML"
msgstr "Obtenir le HTML de l'aperçu du menu rendu"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Returns rendered HTML preview of a menu for the visual builder.\n"
"\n"
"    **Query Parameters:**\n"
"    - `display_type`: Override the menu's display type for preview\n"
"    - `device`: Device type for responsive preview (`desktop`, `tablet`, "
"`mobile`)\n"
"    - `popup`: Set to `1` for full-page popup preview with device frames\n"
"\n"
"    **Use Cases:**\n"
"    - Live preview in menu builder (JSON mode)\n"
"    - Full-screen popup preview (popup mode)\n"
"\n"
"    **Authentication:** Staff session required\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Retourne une prévisualisation HTML rendue d'un menu pour le constructeur "
"visuel. **Paramètres de requête :** - `display_type` : Remplace le type "
"d'affichage du menu pour la prévisualisation - `device` : Type d'appareil "
"pour la prévisualisation responsive (`desktop`, `tablet`, `mobile`) - "
"`popup` : Mettre à `1` pour une prévisualisation en popup à page pleine avec "
"des cadres d'appareil **Cas d'utilisation :** - Prévisualisation en temps "
"réel dans le constructeur de menu (mode JSON) - Prévisualisation en popup à "
"écran plein (mode popup) **Authentification :** Session d'employé requise\n"
"    "

msgid "Override display type for preview"
msgstr "Remplacer le type d'affichage pour l'aperçu"

msgid "Device type for responsive preview"
msgstr "Type d'appareil pour l'aperçu adaptatif"

msgid "Return full popup HTML page instead of JSON"
msgstr "Retourner une page HTML complète de popup au lieu de JSON"

msgid "Rendered menu HTML"
msgstr "HTML du menu rendu"

msgid "Get or update menu design tokens"
msgstr "Obtenir ou mettre à jour les jetons de conception du menu"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Gets or updates menu design tokens stored in ThemeBranding.\n"
"\n"
"    These tokens control overall menu styling (colors, spacing, typography)\n"
"    and are shared between the Branding app and Menu Builder.\n"
"\n"
"    **GET Parameters:**\n"
"    - No parameters required\n"
"\n"
"    **POST Body:**\n"
"    ```json\n"
"    {\n"
"        \"tokens\": {\n"
"            \"text-color\": \"#333\",\n"
"            \"text-hover-color\": \"var(--color-primary)\",\n"
"            \"background-hover\": \"var(--color-primary)\",\n"
"            \"item-gap\": \"var(--space-2)\"\n"
"        }\n"
"    }\n"
"    ```\n"
"\n"
"    **Use Cases:**\n"
"    - Load menu tokens in menu builder\n"
"    - Save menu styling changes from menu builder\n"
"    - Sync menu tokens between Branding app and Menu Builder\n"
"\n"
"    **Authentication:** Staff session required\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Gets or updates menu design tokens stored in ThemeBranding.\n"
"\n"
"    These tokens control overall menu styling (colors, spacing, typography)\n"
"    and are shared between the Branding app and Menu Builder.\n"
"\n"
"    **GET Parameters:**\n"
"    - No parameters required\n"
"\n"
"    **POST Body:**\n"
"    ```json\n"
"    {\n"
"        \"tokens\": {\n"
"            \"text-color\": \"#333\",\n"
"            \"text-hover-color\": \"var(--color-primary)\",\n"
"            \"background-hover\": \"var(--color-primary)\",\n"
"            \"item-gap\": \"var(--space-2)\"\n"
"        }\n"
"    }\n"
"    ```\n"
"\n"
"    **Use Cases:**\n"
"    - Load menu tokens in menu builder\n"
"    - Save menu styling changes from menu builder\n"
"    - Sync menu tokens between Branding app and Menu Builder\n"
"\n"
"    **Authentication:** Staff session required\n"
"    "

